<L>__{ext day: don's hospital (spring 1946)}
<A>__{a hospital in new york city. police and teams of private detectives are stationed guarding the area. an ambulance with a team of detectives and button men guards exit the hospital with rifles in hand; followed by several hospital assistants wheeling a hospital stretcher, presumably carrying the don. tessio and clemenza emerge, with other button men bringing up the rear. hagen walks with the stretcher, and for a moment they disappear behind the ambulance. then suddenly, siren blasting, it speeds off, accompanied by dark low slung cars.}
